{
  "stem": "17606.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They knew my background, so they gave me right away my rank back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The whole time, we participated in several actions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Polish-- the Armia Krajowa was one of the best organized.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They worked with the Polish exile government in London, with the Sikorski group.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "As you know, there were three different organizations in Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "One was the PAL, the Polish folks' army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was AL, the army-- the folks' army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "One was more left-- and the AL was strictly communist group.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The one was something in between.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then this was the main organization, was the army of the land, of which I was a member.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Many-- I participated in many actions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The most important action, which I was-- got decorated for it, was the execution of Himmler's brother in law, Kuczera.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Kuczera took charge of the police at the Gestapo in Warsaw in the beginning of 1944.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he was responsible for thousands of deaths.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He just had all the-- hanged them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Hanged them on this terrace, hanged them on this terr-- many priests.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they decide to liquidate him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I was in charge of the retreat group, to cover the retreats.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "One day, it was June.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I don't remember the date if you kill me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The date was set that Kuczera has to be liquidated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We knew that he will take a stroll in a car-- in an open car on the Poniatowski bridge, which connected to the outskirts of Praga with central Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we were supposed to liquidate him on that bridge, because he was surrounded by Gestapo from all the sides.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we-- as he came, it was around noon time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He came over the bridge.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
